  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWORDCAR is an automotive combat game with a fresh coat of gore.  Master physics based combat, pull off eviscerating drifts and cast punishing spells in this unique CAR-acter action game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those A-Holes at BUSY CORP are at it again. It's time to rip off their grubby fingers and release their parasitic clutch on SWORDCITY. Liberate humanity with a two-ton sword that THRIVES on the blood of the soulless busymen. Crush the hellish company metropolis and put your blade to the CEO. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave a trail of limbs in your wake employing a wide range of cars, medieval weaponry and diabolical BLOOD MAGIK.  Terrifying gore powered machines will hunt you down every step of the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWORDCAR is an automotive combat game with a fresh coat of gore.  Master physics based combat, pull off eviscerating drifts and cast punishing spells in this unique CAR-acter action game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/7d6b843a592bdef3da01cd02ddd3d55d.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those A-Holes at BUSY CORP are at it again. It's time to rip off their grubby fingers and release their parasitic clutch on SWORDCITY. Liberate humanity with a two-ton sword that THRIVES on the blood of the soulless busymen. Crush the hellish company metropolis and put your blade to the CEO. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/69151fb6b76f1c15b306e9421f84f8b6.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave a trail of limbs in your wake employing a wide range of cars, medieval weaponry and diabolical BLOOD MAGIK.  Terrifying gore powered machines will hunt you down every step of the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.poster.avif?t=1763581343\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.webm?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517770/extras/c5b750fdf551a2c712973b77f423e7a4.mp4?t=1763581343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
